line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">Collecte des relevés bancaires</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;color:#0D0D0D\"> : Obtenez les relevés bancaires de la période à rapprocher,\r\nhabituellement mensuelle. Ces relevés doivent être téléchargés ou obtenus\r\ndirectement auprès de la banque et comprennent toutes les transactions traitées\r\nsur le compte bancaire de l\'entreprise.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">Préparation des enregistrements internes</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;color:#0D0D0D\"> : Rassemblez les enregistrements comptables\r\ninternes de l\'entreprise, y compris les registres de caisse, les journaux\r\ncomptables et tout autre document contenant des informations sur les\r\ntransactions financières, telles que les dépôts, les paiements, les frais bancaires,\r\netc.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">Établissement des soldes de départ</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;color:#0D0D0D\"> : Déterminez le solde de départ pour le\r\nrapprochement bancaire en utilisant le dernier solde de compte bancaire\r\ndisponible à partir des enregistrements internes de l\'entreprise.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">Comparaison des transactions</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;color:#0D0D0D\"> : Passez en revue les transactions enregistrées\r\ndans les livres comptables de l\'entreprise et comparez-les avec celles figurant\r\nsur le relevé bancaire. Associez chaque transaction dans les enregistrements\r\ninternes avec une transaction correspondante sur le relevé bancaire.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">Identification des différences</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;color:#0D0D0D\"> : Identifiez les écarts entre les enregistrements\r\ninternes et les relevés bancaires. Les écarts peuvent être dus à des dépôts ou\r\ndes paiements non enregistrés, des erreurs de saisie, des frais bancaires, des\r\nchèques non déposés, etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">Ajouts et soustractions</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\"> : Ajoutez ou soustrayez les écarts identifiés au solde de\r\ndépart pour obtenir un solde ajusté. Par exemple, si un chèque émis par\r\nl\'entreprise n\'a pas encore été encaissé par la banque, ajoutez-le au solde ajusté.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">Finalisation du rapprochement</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;color:#0D0D0D\"> : Répétez les étapes précédentes jusqu\'à ce que\r\ntous les écarts soient identifiés et ajustés, et que le solde ajusté\r\ncorresponde au solde figurant sur le relevé bancaire. Cela confirme que les\r\nenregistrements comptables internes concordent avec les transactions bancaires.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-indent: -18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">8.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D\">Documentation et archivage</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;color:#0D0D0D\"> : Documentez soigneusement le processus de\r\nrapprochement, y compris les ajustements effectués, et archivez tous les\r\ndocuments pertinents, tels que les relevés bancaires, les enregistrements\r\ncomptables, les justificatifs d\'ajustements, etc., pour référence future et\r\npour les besoins d\'audit.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Tout le monde', 'Cours', 'FORMATION643766307881', 'Actif');
